Jamel PICKKEY
v.
LOUISIANA DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY & CORRECTIONS, et al. NO. 2018-CT-1065 Supreme Court of Louisiana. September 21, 2018

*493WRIT NOT CONSIDERED. Petitioner has not demonstrated that petitioner sought review in the court(s) below before filing in this Court nor shown the "extraordinary circumstances" that would justify bypassing that level of review. La.S.Ct.R. X § 5(b).
